{# Branch Page #}
<div class="bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="container py-6 md:py-10">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap md:-mx-8">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:px-8 mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <div class="prose-sm md:prose text-primary">
          <h1>Welcome to Branch Page</h1>
          
          <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Cras congue odio urna, eu pulvinar elit fermentum et. Sed convallis fringilla velit. Integer at orci at eros ullamcorper lacinia ac.</p>

          <ul>
            <li>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet</li>
            <li>Sed nec dolor quis arcu suscipit tincidunt</li>
            <li>Fusce mi ipsum, placerat ac eros at</li>
          </ul>
          
          <p>Sed nec dolor quis arcu suscipit tincidunt. Nullam consectetur justo quis volutpat fringilla. Phasellus at lobortis metus, ac pulvinar ligula. Fusce mi ipsum, placerat ac eros at, fermentum facilisis nulla. Etiam quis dui ex.</p>

          <p>Aenean ac sem a ligula aliquam fermentum. Maecenas at felis eu tortor sodales ultricies. Praesent a pulvinar purus. Nam tincidunt facilisis lobortis.</p>
        </div>
      </div> 

      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 md:px-8">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap">
          <div class="bg-primary{{ map ? ' w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-full lg:w-1/2' : ' w-full' }}">
            <span class="block text-white font-bold text-lg md:text-xl xl:text-2xl px-6 md:px-8 pt-6 md:pt-8 pb-4">Opening Times</span>
            <ul class="pb-8">
              {% for day in openingTimes.days %}
                <li class="flex px-6 md:px-8 py-2 md:py-3 text-white {{ loop.index % 2 == 1 ? ' ' : ' bg-primary-dark' }}">
                  <span class="block opacity-50">{{ day.title }}</span>
                  <span class="block ml-auto text-sm uppercase leading-wider">
                    {% if day.open and day.close %}
                      {{ day.open}} - {{ day.close}}
                    {% else %}
                      Closed
                    {% endif %}
                  </span>
                </li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </div>
          {% if map %}
            <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 md:w-full lg:w-1/2">
              <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="{{ map }}" frameborder="0" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" aria-hidden="false" tabindex="0"></iframe>
            </div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>